## Neo4j Brand Shapes Guidelines

Reference: https://neo4j.design/40a8cff71/p/995201-brand-shapes

### Core Shape Elements

**Nodes (Circles)**
- Primary representation of graph nodes
- Use filled circles with 2px stroke
- Standard sizes: 40px, 60px, 80px diameter
- Color: Mid Baltic (#014063) or category-specific colors

**Relationships (Lines/Arrows)**
- Connect nodes with directional arrows
- Arrow style: Filled triangle head
- Line weight: 2px
- Color: Slate (#485662) or contextual colors

**Containers (Rounded Rectangles)**
- Group related elements
- Border radius: 8px
- Stroke: 2px, Mid Baltic (#014063)
- Fill: Light Gray (#F5F7FA) or transparent

